@startuml UC_06_View_Activity_History
title UC-06: View Activity History

|User|
start
:(1) Open the Activity History page;
:(2) Choose a page of history records;

|System|
:(3) Validate authenticated user;
:(4) Fetch paginated post history for the user;
if (Records found?) then (Yes)
  :(5) Return the history list and pagination data;
else (No)
  :(6) Return an empty result;
endif

|User|
:(7) View past posts and interactions;

|System|
:(8) Return the selected history record when requested;

stop
@enduml
